summary: Armor made for the Stormcloak Rangers and archer specialists
descriptionHtml:
[center][IMG]http://i1206.photobucket.com/albums/bb445/FoxyFoxia/StormcloakRangerArmor_zpsc1913be4.png[/IMG][/center]

In continuing with my Stormcloak based armors I wanted to get an armor specifically designed for rangers and people who specialize in Bows and arrows. So I did a little bit of work and put this armor together.

It's craftable under the hide section of the forge. V1.0 is only for the males. a female version will be out later.

Just like the Stormcloak Battle Armor this armor when finished will be incorporated into Call of the North Revisited.

Thanks to:
Guardian300: For original bear helm mesh
Foxia: For the armor itself
